Cut lettuce into 6 wedges. Rinse and wrap in paper towels to remove moisture. Combine ingredients for dressing, mix well, set aside. Put almonds, sugar and cinnamon in a non-stick pan over medium heat. Saute until almonds are slightly brown and sugar dissolves. Be careful not to burn. Allow almonds to cool. Top lettuce wedge with dressing. Garnish with almonds, bell peppers, onion and feta.